Package com.wowza.gocoder.sdk.api.status

Classes used by SDK components to provide detailed state, status, and error information

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    WZStatusCallback
    WZStatusCallback defines an implementation interface for the callback argument to the startStreaming API method used to monitor the status of a broadcast.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    WZState
    The WZState class provides identifiers that indicate the state of various components and operations within the SDK.
    WZStatus
    The WZStatus is a thread-safe class for working with SDK component state and error properties.
